      "text": "会比龙还危险",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 154.48,
      "time_str": "02:34.480",
      "text": "我当然知道这世界",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 156.95,
      "time_str": "02:36.950",
      "text": "不会完美无暇",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
